(Reverse) Abig: Williams

ag''st Geo: Jacobs Sen''r

( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 1, no. 223, Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives, Massachusetts State Archives. Boston, MA. )', ' Testimony of Abigail Williams v. George Jacobs, Sr. ', 'abigail_williams', NULL, 'From a deposition. By George Jacobs Sr. —  Testimony of Abigail Williams v. George Jacobs, Sr. , May 11, 1692 (SWP No. 78.7). Dated 1692-05-11. Testimony of Abigail Williams v. George Jacobs, Sr.', 'SWP No. 78.7', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
