[++ June 3, 1692]

We whose nams are under written: can testiefie if cald to it that goodde nurs have bene trobled with an Infirmity of body for many years which the Juree of women seme to be Afraid it should be something elce.

*Rebecah preson

*Mary Tarbel

( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 1, No. 85, Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives, Massachusetts State Archives. Boston, MA. )', ' Statement of Rebecca Preston & Mary Tarbell for Rebecca Nurse ', 'salem_village_petition_signers_and_witnesses', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Rebecca Nurse —  Statement of Rebecca Preston & Mary Tarbell for Rebecca Nurse  (SWP No. 94.28). Statement of Rebecca Preston & Mary Tarbell for Rebecca Nurse', 'SWP No. 94.28', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
