[+ July 2, 1692]

the deposition of humpry Clark aged about 21 yere saith that about a yere agoo I was asleep and about midnight the bed shook & I awaked and saw a woman stand by the bed side which when I well Looked semed to me to be goodwif wills which jumpid to the tother corner of the house & then I saw hir no more

Jurat in Curia

(Reverse) Humphey Clerk.

( Essex Institute MSS. Collection, no. 8. Peabody Essex Museum, Phillips Library, Roowley, MA. )', ' Deposition of Humphrey Clark v. Sarah Wilds ', 'other_documented_accused', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Sarah Wilds —  Deposition of Humphrey Clark v. Sarah Wilds  (SWP No. 136.12). Deposition of Humphrey Clark v. Sarah Wilds', 'SWP No. 136.12', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
