[+ September 14, 1692]

The tistimony of Thomas Chandler aged about 65 who saith that I have often hard Samuell wardle of Andovr till yung person thire fortine and he was much adicted to that and mayd sport of it and farther said not

Jurat in Curia. (Reverse) Thomas Chandler depo agst Sam''l Wardwell

( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 2, no. 60, Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives, Massachusetts State Archives, Boston, MA. )', 'Testimony of Thomas Chandler v. Samuel Wardwell ', 'samuel_wardwell', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Samuel Wardwell — Testimony of Thomas Chandler v. Samuel Wardwell  (SWP No. 133.6). Testimony of Thomas Chandler v. Samuel Wardwell', 'SWP No. 133.6', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
