[September 15, 1692]

The Deposition of Sarah Coalman , who saith, about the fivetenth of August last past that she was tormented three or four times by Marget Scot , of Rowly, or her appearance, by pricking, pinching, and choaking of me, and I do verily believe that she is a witch. Sarah Coleman affirmed before te Grand Inquest, that the above written Evidence is truth, uppon her oath 15th September, 1692.

( Thomas Gage, The History of Rowley. (Boston: Ferdinand Andres, 1840) 174-175.', 'Deposition of Sarah Coleman Vs. Margaret Scott ', 'margaret_scott', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Margaret Scott — Deposition of Sarah Coleman Vs. Margaret Scott , September 15, 1692 (SWP No. 119.9). Dated 1692-09-15. Deposition of Sarah Coleman Vs. Margaret Scott', 'SWP No. 119.9', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
