[+ April 19, 1692]

The deposistion of prisceller chub aged about 31: years, this deponent testifieth and saith that sum time the last winter I was a discoursing with Abigaill Hobbs about her wicked cariges and disobedience to hir father and Mother and she tould me she did not care what any body said to hir for she had seen the divell and had made a covenant or bargin with him.

( W. Elliot Woodward, Records of Salem Witchcraft, 2 vols. (Privately printed, Roxbury, MA: 1864) Vol. 1, pp. 177–78. )', ' Deposition of Priscilla Chub v. Abigail Hobbs ', 'priscilla_trask', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Abigail Hobbs —  Deposition of Priscilla Chub v. Abigail Hobbs  (SWP No. 69.7). Deposition of Priscilla Chub v. Abigail Hobbs', 'SWP No. 69.7', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565647, 1775266565647, 0);
