[+ March 24, 1692]

The Deposistion of Mercy lewes aged about 19 years who testifieth and saith that on the 3d April 1692 the Apperishtion of Dorrithy good Sarah goods daughter came to me and did afflect me urging me to writ in hir book and seuerall times sence Dorithy good hath afflected me by biting pinching and choaking me urging me to writ in hir book.

(Reverse) Mercy Lewis against

Dorothy. Good .

( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 1, no. 62. Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives, Massachusetts Statte Archive, MA. )', ' Mercy Lewis v. Dorothy Good ', 'mercy_lewis', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Dorothy Good —  Mercy Lewis v. Dorothy Good  (SWP No. 62.3). Mercy Lewis v. Dorothy Good', 'SWP No. 62.3', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565648, 1775266565648, 0);
