( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 2, no. 173. Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives. Massachusetts State Archives, Boston. MA )', 'Order of Mary Post for Payment ', 'salem_village_petition_signers_and_witnesses', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Reversal of Attainder — Order of Mary Post for Payment , January 7, 1712 (SWP No. 173.53). Dated 1712-01-07. Order of Mary Post for Payment', 'SWP No. 173.53', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565648, 1775266565648, 0);
