February 18th 1711/12

( Essex County Court Archives, Salem -- Witchcraft Vol. 2. no. 144. Massachusetts Supreme Judicial Court, Judicial Archives. Massachusetts State Archives, Boston, MA )', 'Order of Elizabeth Very for Payment, Cases of John Proctor & Elizabeth Proctor ', 'elizabeth_proctor', NULL, 'From a deposition. By Reversal of Attainder — Order of Elizabeth Very for Payment, Cases of John Proctor & Elizabeth Proctor , February 18, 1712 (SWP No. 173.68). Dated 1712-02-18. Order of Elizabeth Very for Payment, Cases of John Proctor & Elizabeth Proctor', 'SWP No. 173.68', 'salem_project', 1.0, NULL, 1775266565648, 1775266565648, 0);
